    <value>Navigate to 'Backup Jobs'. Click the add button to define a new task. You must provide a unique name, a valid source directory, and a target destination. Choose between 'Full' (complete copy) or 'Differential' (only changed files).</value>
  </data>
    <data name="Step2_Title" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>2. Security &amp; Encryption Whitelist</value>
  </data>
